		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Am I &#8220;unclean&#8221; in some way because my highest ambition is to learn Bass riffs to my favorite songs by TAB?  I&#8217;m an old man with a Great Fender Aerodyne Bass?  Most of you will surpass my abilities and skill in about 20 minutes&#8230;&#8230;.I&#8217;m 70&#8230;&#8230;I love the Bass and it&#8217;s place in music more than anyone I know&#8230;.including those who have a lot of life and time and passion to spend.  All I can ever hope for is the most basic of basics, but I have a firm grasp of who and what I&#8217;m capable of, ( very little).  I&#8217;ve had Fender Fever since I was 14 years old&#8230;&#8230;1960.  Still, I smile every time I hear a Bassline, and am as happy to hear it as the Best of the Best&#8230;&#8230;.JPR</p>
